comments: Kuminga (GSW) is moving alongside Dosunmu's (CHI) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Green (GSW) and Kuminga (GSW) engage with one another, and marginal contact occurs as Dosunmu (CHI) moves over the pick.
Dosunmu (CHI) slides his hand across Green's (GSW) upper body, and the contact during the pick is marginal.
Moody (GSW) and DeRozan (CHI) come together at the same spot, and the contact at the end of the drive is marginal.
Kuminga (GSW) is firming up in Dosunmu's (CHI) path and he absorbs the contact to his upper body.
Green (GSW) does not establish himself in Caruso's (CHI) path and delivers contact with his side that dislodges Caruso.
Moody (GSW) moves alongside DeRozan's (CHI) path and legally contests DeRozan's shot attempt.
Paul (GSW) briefly grasps Dosunmu's (CHI) arm and Paul releases Dosunmu as he moves to navigate the screen.
Jackson-Davis (GSW) establishes himself with his arm slightly extended in Dosunmu's (CHI) path, and the contact is marginal.
Kuminga (GSW) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward DeRozan (CHI), and is not in a legal guarding position as body contact occurs during DeRozan's upward shooting motion.
Paul (GSW) establishes himself in White's (CHI) path and does not deliver contact during the pick.
Jackson-Davis (GSW) turns to roll towards the basket, and marginal contact occurs with White (CHI) as the defensive switch occurs.
White (CHI) briefly places his hand against Jackson-Davis' (GSW) side and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Jackson-Davis (GSW) establishes himself in Vucevic's (CHI) path, and he gives Vucevic the time and distance to avoid the contact.
Vucevic (CHI) places a resting forearm to Podziemski's (GSW) back and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Jackson-Davis (GSW) commits a take foul on Vucevic (CHI).
Paul (GSW) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Paul (GSW) does not step on the sideline when he receives the ball.
Thompson (GSW) commits a take foul on DeRozan (CHI).
